targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  MEA_DATE AS "time",
  MEA_VALUE1 AS "$mea_type_1"
FROM gam_measurement
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(MEA_DATE) AND
  MEA_OBJECT_ID = $object
ORDER BY MEA_DATE

SELECT
  MEA_DATE AS "time",
  MEA_VALUE2 AS "$mea_type_2"
FROM gam_measurement
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(MEA_DATE) AND
  MEA_OBJECT_ID = $object
ORDER BY MEA_DATE

SELECT
  MEA_DATE AS "time",
  MEA_VALUE3 AS "$mea_type_3"
FROM gam_measurement
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(MEA_DATE) AND
  MEA_OBJECT_ID = $object
ORDER BY MEA_DATE

SELECT
  MEA_DATE AS "time",
  MEA_VALUE4 AS "$mea_type_4"
FROM gam_measurement
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(MEA_DATE) AND
  MEA_OBJECT_ID = $object
ORDER BY MEA_DATE

SELECT
  MEA_DATE AS "time",
  MEA_VALUE5 AS "$mea_type_5"
FROM gam_measurement
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(MEA_DATE) AND
  MEA_OBJECT_ID = $object
ORDER BY MEA_DATE
